<db:title>[static] int QScatter3DSeries::invalidSelectionIndex()</db:title>
<db:para>Returns an invalid index for selection. This index is set to the <db:link xlink:href="qscatter3dseries-qtdatavis.xml#selectedItem-prop">selectedItem</db:link> property to clear the selection from this series.</db:para>
